OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776204665
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion risk points
OL,4,Cdeduction after charge over their
OL,5,Cfinances
OL,7,FWest Bromwich Albion say they consider
OL,8,Fto have 'fully complied' with Profit
OL,9,Fand Sustainability (P&S) rules
OL,10,Ffollowing reports they risk a points
OL,11,Fdeduction.
OL,13,FThe club could face a points sanction
OL,14,Fthis season over a potential breach of
OL,15,Fthe EFL's financial rules, according
OL,16,Fto reports.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776204665
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion risk points
OL,4,Cdeduction after charge over their
OL,5,Cfinances
OL,7,FThe Championship team are only two
OL,8,Fpoints above the relegation zone,
OL,9,Ftherefore any points deducted could be
OL,10,Fvery costly in West Brom's bid to stay
OL,11,Fin the division.
OL,13,FHowever, the points deduction may only
OL,14,Fapply for next season (2026/27),
OL,15,Fdepending on how the charge from the
OL,16,FEnglish Football League is applied.
OL,18,FWest Brom responded to the reports in
OL,19,Fa statement today: "The club considers
OL,20,Fthat it has fully complied with the
OL,21,FP&S rules.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776204665
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion risk points
OL,4,Cdeduction after charge over their
OL,5,Cfinances
OL,7,F"The club will continue to co-operate
OL,8,Fwith the EFL's Club Financial
OL,9,FReporting Unit and looks forward to
OL,10,Fresolving this matter."
OL,12,FThe Telegraph was first to report on
OL,13,FMonday morning that the Club Financial
OL,14,FReporting Unit (CFRU) had filed a
OL,15,Fcompliance report to the Baggies over
OL,16,Fa breach of the loss limits for the
OL,17,F2024-25 season under the EFL's
OL,18,Fprofitability and sustainability rules.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776204665
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion risk points
OL,4,Cdeduction after charge over their
OL,5,Cfinances
OL,7,FIt's understood that under sanctioning
OL,8,Fguidelines, sanctions should be
OL,9,Fapplied in the season after breach `
OL,10,Fwhich would mean if a points penalty
OL,11,Fwere imposed it would affect Albion's
OL,12,Fpoints total this season.
OL,14,FThat could have a significant impact
OL,15,Fon the club, who sit 20th in the Sky
OL,16,FBet Championship.
OL,18,FThe Telegraph also reported that
OL,19,FAlbion are seeking to delay any
OL,20,Fpunishment until next season.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776204665
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion risk points
OL,4,Cdeduction after charge over their
OL,5,Cfinances
OL,7,FOther sanctions that could be imposed
OL,8,Fare a transfer ban or a fine. As a
OL,9,Fclub that competed in the Championship
OL,10,Flast season, West Brom were required
OL,11,Fto submit their annual accounts for
OL,12,F2024-25 by December 31, 2025. Accounts
OL,13,Fof all clubs are assessed for
OL,14,Fcompliance.
OL,16,FIt is understood West Brom have 14
OL,17,Fdays from receipt of the CFRU
OL,18,Fcompliance report to file a response,
OL,19,Fand any hearing should usually take
OL,20,Fplace within 28 days of the compliance
OL,21,Freport being submitted.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776204665
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion risk points
OL,4,Cdeduction after charge over their
OL,5,Cfinances
OL,7,FDecisions taken over sanctions by the
OL,8,FClub Financial Reporting Panel (CFRP)
OL,9,Fare usually published, but prior to
OL,10,Fthat discussions between a club and
OL,11,Fthe EFL remain strictly confidential.
OL,13,FIn a full statement, the club said:
OL,14,F"West Bromwich Albion acknowledges
OL,15,Fmedia reports relating to the club's
OL,16,Fcompliance with the EFL's
OL,17,FProfitability & Sustainability (P&S)
OL,18,Frules.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776204665
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion risk points
OL,4,Cdeduction after charge over their
OL,5,Cfinances
OL,7,F"The club considers that it has fully
OL,8,Fcomplied with the P&S rules. The club
OL,9,Fwill continue to co-operate with the
OL,10,FEFL's Club Financial Reporting Unit
OL,11,Fand looks forward to resolving this
OL,12,Fmatter.
OL,14,F"Albion understands the concerns of
OL,15,Fsupporters and thanks fans for their
OL,16,Funwavering support of the team, whose
OL,17,Fsuccess on the pitch during the final
OL,18,Ffour games of the season remains our
OL,19,Fabsolute priority.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
