CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776204665
OL,3,CWest Bromwich Albion risk points
OL,4,Cdeduction after charge over their
OL,5,Cfinances
OL,7,F"It would not be appropriate for the
OL,8,Fclub to comment further at this stage."
OL,10,FThe EFL has been approached for
OL,11,Fcomment.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
